    Frequently Asked Questions

    Frequently Asked Questions

    How do I take this supplement?

    Take two gummies per day, preferably with food, to support absorption and effectiveness. Consistent daily use is recommended for best results.

    When can I expect to see results?

     Most users begin noticing improvements in energy, focus, and performance within 2 to 4 weeks of regular use. Results may vary depending on individual health and lifestyle.

    Is it safe to take with other supplements or medications?

     Yes, our formula is designed to be safe and non-reactive. However, if you are taking prescription medications or have a medical condition, we recommend consulting your healthcare provider before use.

     Are there any side effects?

     When taken as directed, side effects are rare. In high doses, some individuals may experience mild gastrointestinal discomfort. Always follow the recommended dosage.

    Where is your Shilajit sourced from?

     Our Shilajit is sustainably harvested from the Himalayan region at high altitudes and undergoes purification and quality testing to ensure potency and safety.
